'''月事假'''是指當[[女性|女性]]因[[月事|月事]]不適而無法工作時，便可選擇享有的有薪或無薪假期。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://classprojects.kenyon.edu/wmns/Wmns36/bloodflow/legal.htm#leave|title=menstrual leave|author=classprojects|access-date=2016-09-21|archive-date=2016-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160506024239/http://classprojects.kenyon.edu/wmns/Wmns36/bloodflow/legal.htm#leave|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://cleanclothes.org/newslist/252-labour-rights-in-indonesia-what-is-menstruation-leave |title=what is menstruation leave |author=cleanclothes |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110813171350/http://cleanclothes.org/newslist/252-labour-rights-in-indonesia-what-is-menstruation-leave |archivedate=2011-08-13 }}</ref> 目前，月事假仍備受爭議，包括被指涉及[[性別歧視|性別歧視]]、影響生產力等。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://lipmag.com/culture/menstrual-leave-delightful-or-discriminatory/|title=Menstrual leave: delightful or discriminatory?|accessdate=3 January 2014|last=Iuliano|first=Sarah|work=5 August 2013|publisher=Lip Magazine|archive-date=2019-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190327090204/http://lipmag.com/culture/menstrual-leave-delightful-or-discriminatory/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.salon.com/2006/10/11/menstruation_4/|title=Should women get paid menstruation leave?|last=Price|first=Catherine|date=11 October 2006|newspaper=Salon|accessdate=3 January 2014|archive-date=2019-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190327123049/https://www.salon.com/2006/10/11/menstruation_4/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 歷史 ==
月事假的概念早於20世紀初的[[日本|日本]]出現。1920年代，日本有勞工團體為在職女性爭取生理假。 1947年，日本正式立[[法|法]]實行月事假，其後部分國家包括南韓、台灣及印尼都陸續立法容許女性來經時可放假休息。 <ref>{{Cite journal|title=Japan's 1986 Equal Employment Opportunity Law and the Changing Discourse on Gender|author=JSTOR|volume=20|pages=268–302|jstor=3174950}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://gradworks.umi.com/32/65/3265147.html|title=Periodic struggles: Menstruation leave in modern Japan|author=HARVARD UNIVERSITY, 2007|access-date=2016-09-21|archive-date=2012-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120323084131/http://gradworks.umi.com/32/65/3265147.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 現今變遷 ==
2007年，運動用品公司[[Nike|Nike]]亦在其[[行為守則|行為守則]]中引入月事假，適用於全球所有地區的分部，並與其他合作伙伴簽署備忘，要求他們跟隨有關標準。 <ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.apparelsearch.com/education/research/child_labor_clothing/child_labor_fashion_industry_2005/V_Apparel_Appendices/Surveys_from_companies/Nike.htm|title=NIKE Policy|author=apparelsearch|access-date=2016-09-21|archive-date=2019-08-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190831040953/https://www.apparelsearch.com/education/research/child_labor_clothing/child_labor_fashion_industry_2005/v_apparel_appendices/surveys_from_companies/nike.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref> 2016年，英國社企Coexist准許女員工在有需要時放月事假，成為首間設有月事假的英國企業。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/newsitems/200502/s1300583.htm|title=Unions seek 'menstrual leave' for Toyota workers|author=abc|access-date=2016-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110512155215/http://www.abc.net.au/news/newsitems/200502/s1300583.htm|archive-date=2011-05-12|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

== 各國立法情況 ==
[[香港|香港]]未有立法規定月事假，[[公務員事務局|公務員事務局]]甚不積極爭取，[[街坊工友服務處|街坊工友服務處]]梁耀忠表示：部分[[男性|男性]]反對月事假。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E5%8D%80%E5%B0%88%E9%A1%8C/165621/%E7%94%9F%E7%90%86%E5%81%87-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%82%8A%E5%BA%A6%E8%BF%94%E5%B7%A5%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%88%E7%B6%93%E5%81%87-nike%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E6%9C%89%E5%81%87-%E7%8D%A8%E6%BC%8F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF|title=【生理假】香港邊度返工有月經假？Nike全球有假，獨漏香港？|publisher=[[香港01|香港01]]|date=2018-03-07|5=|accessdate=2019-01-05|archive-date=2019-08-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190823232350/https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E5%8D%80%E5%B0%88%E9%A1%8C/165621/%E7%94%9F%E7%90%86%E5%81%87-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%82%8A%E5%BA%A6%E8%BF%94%E5%B7%A5%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%88%E7%B6%93%E5%81%87-nike%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E6%9C%89%E5%81%87-%E7%8D%A8%E6%BC%8F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在[[台灣|台灣]]，《[[性別工作平等法|性別工作平等法]]》規定女性僱員若因生理日而導致工作有困難，每月可請1天生理假，每年可請3天生理假。若全年病假總天數不超過30天，將可獲支付半薪。但如果30天病假都請完，仍可再請3天生理假，但3天生理假將不支薪。請生理假亦不需證明，若僱主要求員工提出生理假證明文件，可能會被罰款。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.chinapost.com.tw/taiwan/national/national-news/2013/11/27/394603/Gender-equality.htm|title=Gender equality in employment act revised|author=The China Post|access-date=2016-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161028163606/http://www.chinapost.com.tw/taiwan/national/national-news/2013/11/27/394603/Gender-equality.htm|archive-date=2016-10-28|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

在[[日本|日本]]，法例表明女性可因月事不適而請假，但並無要求企業提供有薪的月事假或額外支薪予月事期間仍然工作的員工。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.asianfoodworker.net/maternity/UIZensen-model-CBA.pdf|title=Comparison of the Japanese Laws and Model CBA of UI ZENSEN on Maternity Protection|author=asianfoodworker|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070626184404/http://www.asianfoodworker.net/maternity/UIZensen-model-CBA.pdf|archivedate=2007-06-26}}</ref>

在[[南韓|南韓]]，法例規定女性除可享有月事假，更可在放棄月事假，繼續工作時獲得額外工資。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://joongangdaily.joins.com/article/view.asp?aid=2885715|title=Once again, court orders menstrual leave payout|author=joongangdaily|access-date=2016-09-21|archive-date=2012-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120519032627/http://joongangdaily.joins.com/article/view.asp?aid=2885715|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在[[印尼|印尼]]，法例規定女性每月可享有兩天的月事假。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.niew.gov.my/niew/en/download/doc_download/324-labour-act |title=Labour Act |author=Govt. of Indonesia |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111004064721/http://www.niew.gov.my/niew/en/download/doc_download/324-labour-act |archivedate=2011-10-04 }}</ref>

在[[菲律賓|菲律賓]]，法例表明除了孕婦或已停經的女性，所有私人企業及政府女性員工都可享有半薪的月事假。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/breakingnews/nation/view/20080818-155398/Mandatory-menstruation-leave-measure-filed-in-House|title=Mandatory menstruation leave measure filed in House|accessdate=June 16, 2011|author=Maila Ager|date=August 18, 2008|publisher=Inquirer.net|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402075544/http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/breakingnews/nation/view/20080818-155398/Mandatory-menstruation-leave-measure-filed-in-House|archive-date=2015-04-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

[[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]]2013年有建議立法，<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/russian-lawmaker-proposes-paid-days-menstruating-women-495918|title=Menstruation Leave: Russian Lawmaker Proposes Paid Days Off For Women Employees on Period|last=Owoseje|first=Toyin|date=July 31, 2013|newspaper=International Business Times|accessdate=3 January 2014|archive-date=2021-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128043914/https://www.ibtimes.co.uk/russian-lawmaker-proposes-paid-days-menstruating-women-495918|dead-url=no}}</ref> 這建議沒有被接納。<ref>Will Worley (4 January 2017). [https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/africa/zambia-period-day-off-women-menstruation-law-gender-womens-rights-a7509061.html The country where all women get a day off because of their period] {{Wayback|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/africa/zambia-period-day-off-women-menstruation-law-gender-womens-rights-a7509061.html |date=20190827101642 }}. ''[[獨立報|獨立報]]''. [2019-01-05].</ref>

